355
00:17:25,971 --> 00:17:27,199
A bientôt.

356
00:17:32,010 --> 00:17:33,204
Johnny Chase ?

357
00:17:33,845 --> 00:17:35,176
Montre-leur, mec.

358
00:17:38,817 --> 00:17:41,377
- Sheila, ça va?
- Salut, oui. Et toi ?

359
00:17:42,787 --> 00:17:44,049
- Bonjour.
- Le voilà.

360
00:17:44,155 --> 00:17:46,316
- Merci de me recevoir.
- Ca va ?

361
00:17:47,192 --> 00:17:50,457
- Tu me dis quelque chose.
- Tu as déjà auditionné pour moi.

362
00:17:51,396 --> 00:17:53,261
